        <label>FIGURE 1</label>
        <caption>
          <p>Brief summary of fIDBAC database. <bold>(A)</bold> Number of genomes in each phylum. <bold>(B)</bold> Distribution of genome size in the fIDBAC database. <bold>(C)</bold> Distribution of GC content in the fIDBAC database. <bold>(D)</bold> Distribution of pairwise ANI values between any of two assemblies in the fIDBAC database.</p>
        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="fmicb-12-723577-g001" position="float"/>
