            <italic toggle="yes"><sup>a</sup>Expected, the number of query genomes.</italic>
          </p>
        </fn>
        <fn id="t3fn2">
          <p>
            <italic toggle="yes"><sup>b</sup>16S, number of 16S top 1 result that matches the original label.</italic>
          </p>
        </fn>
